--------------------------- RESUME GAME HERE -------------------------
Outside Kade's Middle lifestyle apartment, Renton. 22:30, Sunday February 15, 2080. Rain falling.
Kade stands in the parking lot, holding nothing, looking up at his third-floor window where Mariana and Sofia wait. The van (loaded with military hardware) is parked nearby. Rigs and Sable are unloading the sedan's cargo.
Sable has taken the rabbits upstairs.
The inventory can wait. The appraisal can wait. The next job can wait.
Upstairs is the vault that opens from inside. The family Kade didn't plan to steal. The choice he doesn't know how to make.
The crew awaits his word.
What do you do?
